<section class="ta" data-component="team-alternating"> <div class="ta__inner"> <div class="ta__header"> <p class="ta__eyebrow">Ons team</p> <h2 class="ta__title">Mensen die <em>results</em> leveren</h2> </div> <div class="ta__row"> <div class="ta__photo"> <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=800&q=80" alt="Mark Visscher" loading="lazy"> <div class="ta__quote-card"> <p class="ta__quote-text">"Adverteren zonder data is geld weggooien. Wij maken elke beslissing meetbaar."</p> </div> </div> <div class="ta__content"> <p class="ta__member-role">Founder &amp; Google Ads Specialist</p> <h3 class="ta__member-name">Mark Visscher</h3> <p class="ta__bio">Met 10 jaar in performance marketing heeft Mark meer dan €50M aan Google en Meta ad spend beheerd. Zijn obsessie? Dat elke euro extra omzet oplevert.</p> <div class="ta__facts"> <div class="ta__fact"> <div class="ta__fact-value">10+</div> <div class="ta__fact-label">Jaar ervaring</div> </div><div class="ta__fact"> <div class="ta__fact-value">€50M</div> <div class="ta__fact-label">Ad spend beheerd</div> </div><div class="ta__fact"> <div class="ta__fact-value">200+</div> <div class="ta__fact-label">Klanten geholpen</div> </div> </div> <a href="#" class="ta__linkedin" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"> <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"></path> </svg>
Verbinden op LinkedIn
</a> </div> </div><div class="ta__row ta__row--reversed"> <div class="ta__photo"> <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108755-2616b612b47c?w=800&q=80" alt="Lisa Hoekstra" loading="lazy"> <div class="ta__quote-card"> <p class="ta__quote-text">"Creativiteit zonder conversie is kunst. Wij maken kunst die verkoopt."</p> </div> </div> <div class="ta__content"> <p class="ta__member-role">Creative Director</p> <h3 class="ta__member-name">Lisa Hoekstra</h3> <p class="ta__bio">Lisa combineert design thinking met performance marketing. Ze gelooft dat de beste ads zowel mooi als effectief zijn — en ze bewijst dat dagelijks.</p> <div class="ta__facts"> <div class="ta__fact"> <div class="ta__fact-value">500+</div> <div class="ta__fact-label">Campagnes gebouwd</div> </div><div class="ta__fact"> <div class="ta__fact-value">6</div> <div class="ta__fact-label">Platforms</div> </div><div class="ta__fact"> <div class="ta__fact-value">3</div> <div class="ta__fact-label">Awards gewonnen</div> </div> </div> <a href="#" class="ta__linkedin" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"> <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"></path> </svg>
